lcn / listcontact             Displays your contacts list
 
   Format:
      ;lcn                    Displays the list
 
   Notes:
      The Chat task is used to chat with other players directly via telnet.
         Calls can be placed (or accepted) with any user whose MUD client uses
         the zChat or MudMaster protocols.
      Use ';addcontact' and ';deletecontact' to add or remove contacts from your
         contacts list.
 
   User commands:
      lcn / listcontact
